         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">Aug. 6th ¶ 1892 ¶ My dear Baron ¶  ¶ I regret to say that I have not been able to answer your note sooner, having a bad attack of gout in my right arm &amp; hand, many thanks for the Characeae Pt 1. If it...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="en">92.08.06a</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="en">From [Edward] Ramsay</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="en">Universitetsbibliothek, Handskr. avdl., Lund.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <note xml:id="ftn1" type="footnote" n="1">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <seg style="font-weight: bold; ">To proof.</seg>
                  </p>
               </note>
               <note xml:id="ftn2" type="footnote" n="2">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">MS is attached to the letter: M to O. Nordtedt, 8 August 1892. Letterhead: 'Australian Museum Sydney'.</p>
               </note>Aug. 6th</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">1892</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">My dear Baron</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I regret to say that I have not been able to answer your note sooner, having a bad attack of gout in my right arm &amp; hand, many thanks for the Characeae Pt 1. If it does not come to more that 20/s or 30/s a year I would like to take it — I will try this season to get the <seg style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">Claudea</hi>
               </seg> again, we have only had two or three trawling trips, and nothing worthy of mention among the Algae, was obtained.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I have a few specimens put away some where which I will look up the first chance I get but I have no doubt when the warm weather comes around again, as I know the exact spot I shall be able to send you fresh specimens</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">believe me</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>dear Baron</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>yours sincerely</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ed.P Ramsay</p>
         </div>
      </body>
